scene.message:
Saeko: Congrats on the Snow{nl}
Queen role.{waitkey}{nl}
In our last year of school,{nl}
I finally lost to you, Tomomi.{waitkey}{ret}

Tomomi: Thank you.{nl}
I'll do my best for your{nl}
sake too, Saeko.{waitkey}{clearbox}But I'm nervous{wait_fr:30}...{nl}
that mask...

{nl}
Is it true everyone who's{nl}
played the Queen so far{nl}
got cursed?{waitkey}{ret}

Saeko: What are you saying!{nl}
That's obviously just{nl}
superstition!{waitkey}{clearbox}Keep a bright heart always,{nl}
and even a curse will feel{nl}
unwelcome and flee!{waitkey}{clearbox}You always get swept up in

Saeko: Get a grip!{waitkey}{nl}
You beat me and won the{nl}
lead role!{waitkey}{clearbox}You ought to be happier, or{nl}
I've got no leg to stand on!!{waitkey}{ret}

Drama Member: Whaaat?!{nl}
Senpai, you're being{nl}
fooled by Saeko!{waitkey}{ret}

Drama Member: You don't know!?{nl}
Saeko withdrew her own{nl}
candidacy for the Snow Queen{waitkey}role!{waitkey}{clearbox}Everyone's saying it.{waitkey}{clearbox}That she was scared of the{nl}
mask's curse, so she pushed{nl}
the Snow Queen role onto you,{waitkey}Senpai Tomomi.{waitkey}{ret}

Tomomi: Withdrew...{wait_fr:30}{nl}
because she was scared of{nl}
the curse...{waitkey}A lie!{wait_fr:30}?{waitkey}{clearbox}Even if she really did{nl}
withdraw, surely she was just{nl}
being considerate of me!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm in the same year as{nl}
Saeko, yet...{wait_fr:30} I've never{nl}
gotten a better role{nl}
than her...{waitkey}{ret}

Drama Member: So she let you{nl}
have the spotlight, at least{nl}
for the last one?{waitkey}What a pushover you are,{nl}
Senpai Tomomi.{waitkey}{clearbox}The Snow Queen's the most{nl}
eye-catching role, you know.{waitkey}{clearbox}There's no way anyone'd give{nl}
it to someone else with no{nl}
reason at all.{waitkey}

Saeko: What's wrong, Tomomi?{nl}
Calling me out and then{waitkey}hiding? What's up?{waitkey}{clearbox}Do your best at tomorrow's{nl}
show, my share too.{nl}
I'm counting on you.{waitkey}{ret}
